</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:TetMap.jpg" class="image" title="TetMap.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/ba/TetMap.jpg/300px-TetMap.jpg" width="300" height="387" border="0" /></a><br />
Some communist targets during the Tet Offensive</td>
</tr>
