<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1968-01-30"><a href="/wiki/January_30" title="January 30">30 January</a> <a href="/wiki/1968" title="1968">1968</a></span> - <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1968-09-23"><a href="/wiki/September_23" title="September 23">23 September</a> <a href="/wiki/1968" title="1968">1968</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Location</th>
<td><span class="location"><a href="/wiki/South_Vietnam" title="South Vietnam">South Vietnam</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Result</th>
<td>US and South Vietnamese military victory.
<p>North Vietnamese propaganda victory.</p>
</td>
