<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;">~323,000 - 595,000<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Casualties and losses</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="50%" style="border-right: 1px dotted #aaa;"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_South_Vietnam.svg" class="image" title="Flag of South Vietnam.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/Flag_of_South_Vietnam.svg/22px-Flag_of_South_Vietnam.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" /></a><br />
<b>Phase I</b>: 2,788 killed, 8,299 wounded, 587 missing<br />
<b>Phase II</b>: 143 killed, 646 wounded<br />
<b>Phase III</b>: unknown<br />
<b>Civilian</b>: 14,000 killed, 24,000 wounded
<p><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_the_United_States.svg" class="image" title="Flag of the United States.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a4/Flag_of_the_United_States.svg/22px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" width="22" height="12" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_South_Korea.svg" class="image" title="Flag of South Korea.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Flag_of_South_Korea.svg/22px-Flag_of_South_Korea.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg" class="image" title="Flag of New Zealand.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg/22px-Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" /></a> <a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Australia.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Australia.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Flag_of_Australia.svg/22px-Flag_of_Australia.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" /></a><br />
<b>Phase I</b>: 1,536 killed, 7,764 wounded, 11 missing<br />
<b>Phase II</b>: 1,161 killed, 3,954 wounded<br />
<b>Phase III</b>: 700 killed, wounded unknown<br />
<b>Total Allied military</b>:<br />
~28,176 casualties<br />
6,328 killed (approximate), 20,663 wounded (approximate), 1,185 missing<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2" title=""><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
</td>
<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;"><b>Total</b>: ~75,000+ killed and wounded (estimate)<sup id="cite_ref-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-3" title=""><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
