s</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Linebacker_II" title="Operation Linebacker II">Linebacker II</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Homecoming" title="Operation Homecoming">Homecoming</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Baby_Lift" title="Operation Baby Lift" class="mw-redirect">Baby Lift</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Eagle_Pull" title="Operation Eagle Pull">Eagle Pull</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Frequent_Wind" title="Operation Frequent Wind">Frequent Wind</a></i></p>
